cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.SI 

The paper discusses the cyber threats and attacks in IoT networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The proposed framework uses a distributed diagnosis system and critical data sharing protocol, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and software engineering (cs.SE) techniques. The approach also focuses on establishing trust between network entities and IoT devices, which is related to social and information networks (cs.SI).
